               <msContents>
                  <summary/>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i0">
                     <locus from="1v" to="16v">1v-16v</locus>
                     <textLang xml:lang="ar">Arabic</textLang>
                     <title type="apodous" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT0049IHA#s15IHA">قران, Eighth ǧuz’ (8/30)</title>
                     <incipit xml:lang="ar">
                        <locus target="#1v">-1v</locus>وَلَوْ أَنًّنَا نَزَلْنَا إِلَيْهِمِ المَلَايكَةَ وَكَلَّمَهُمُ ألمَوْتَيْ وَحَشَرْنَا عَلَيْهُمْ كُل شَئٍ قُبُلًا </incipit>
                     <explicit xml:lang="ar">
                        <locus target="#16v">-16v</locus>فَأَوْفُوْا الكَيْلَ وَالمِيْزَاَنَ وَلَا تَبْخَثُوْا اليَّسَ أَشْيَأَهُمْ<note>Note "تَبْخَثُوْا" instead of "تَبْخَسُوْا".</note>
                     </explicit>
                     <note>6:111-7:85, the text ends in the middle of verse 7:85. Red triple dots or single dots as verse markers. Curve of final nūn-s, and fā'-s in a shape of a more than 90° angle with a thick stroke. Vocalization in a lighter black ink. Rubricated titles of suras. Some letters or sentences enhanced using red ink. Ihmāl marks (rā’-s). Some extensions of letters and words into the margin. Many words completed on the following line. Deletions in black and in red. On fol. 8, the correct form is written in red in the margin.  Other corrections in the margins. Folio 8 is loose and partly torn. Very few catchwords.</note>
                     <note/>
                  </msItem>
               </msContents>
